                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Espresso Résilient</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Un espresso riche et intense, parfait pour revivre les moments forts de l'histoire.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-success">Commander</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                    <img src="https://external-content.duckduckgo.com/iu/?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.galbani.fr%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2FCroissants-sucr%25C3%25A9s_153415341-2.jpeg&f=1&nofb=1&ipt=1660096ebd774f94fb3e6a50479dc96671a3efd34cca6ff335c18031bc4e6f79&ipo=images" class="card-img-top" alt="Croissant">
